thread.title: U.C.L.A. Player Arrested in Rape Case
thread.title_full: U.C.L.A. Player Arrested in Rape Case - The New York Times

author: The Associated Press
title: U.C.L.A. Player Arrested in Rape Case
text:
Adam Searl, 20, a walk-on punter for No. 20 U.C.L.A. , has been arrested in a rape investigation, the Los Angeles police and university officials said.
In October 2014, a U.C.L.A. student reported that she had awakened to find Searl sexually assaulting her after he had returned home with her after an off-campus party, the police said.
